Created by: Lightnet

Information: Portable Game created in java format.
JME 3 that will be use as base for the game. Support by their network.

There will be three part of the program. One is the main server that deal with many type of area in coding wise.
Servers are to host and user are able to chat in lobby and the world is pvp and non pvp.
Clients are able to host their own within their portable devices.

It will be divide into project and will share the same library to made the server configures and as well for the main server.